    "It follows a structure similar to GPT (Generative Pretrained Transformer) 37, which relies on stacked attention layers to process and generate text.",
    "These layers work by focusing on different parts of the input text to determine what is important and what is not.",
    "This mechanism enables Llama 2 to process and generate text effectively, understanding the context and nuances of the input text.",
    "Available in different sizes, from smaller versions like Llama 2 7B to the largest, Llama 2 70B, these variants differ in their processing power and the depth of understanding they can provide.",
